intro: Don't follow the squeak — it follows you.
description:
You find yourself trapped in the endless maze of the Backrooms — but you’re not alone. Somewhere in the humming corridors, something strange waddles in the dark. A duck…

What begins as a simple search for an exit quickly turns into a survival chase. Sometimes you hear soft footsteps… sometimes a quiet squeak right behind you.
The deeper you go, the weirder it gets: distorted rooms, looping hallways, impossible spaces, and the unsettling presence of the duck that always seems one step closer.

Stay alert, navigate the shifting rooms, and outsmart the creature hunting you.
Run when you must. Hide when you can.
And whatever you do, don’t look back when you hear the squeak.
